ttle \n\ninterest or pleasure in doing things?\u201d \no  Patient: \u201cI\u2019m not interested in doing much. I just don\u2019t feel like it. I used to enjoy visiting with friends, \n\nbut I don\u2019t do that much anymore. I\u2019m just not interested.\u201d \n\no  Assessing clinician: \u201cIn the past two weeks, how often would you say you have been bothered by this? \n\nWould you say never or 1 day, 2-6 days, 7-11 days, or 12-14 days?\u201d \n\no  Patient: \u201c7-11 days.\u201d", "type": "Document"}}